</div>

<div class="section">
	<hr/>
	<a title="6" class="bookmark" name="6"></a>
	<p><strong>How long can a new facility operate without a certificate?</strong></p>
	<p>A facility must apply for a certificate of registration within 30 days of beginning use of radiation machines. Facilities utilizing Accelerators over 1 MV; Electronic Brachytherapy Systems; perform Mobile x-ray; or Self-Referred Screening shall have a Certificate of Registration prior to use.</p>
</div>

